---
title: Tex-Mex Cannellini Bean Quesadillas with Zingy Corn Salsa & Chipotle Yoghurt
description: Cannellini beans, Cheddar and carrot unite to make a hearty and delicious filling for these quesadillas. Simply spoon the cheesy
filling onto tortillas, fold them in half and bake. Easy cheesy dinner coming right up!
